    "This integration is essential for a comprehensive food systems management approach, allowing seamless cross-referencing and holistic analysis of the supply chain, from production to consumption [195].",
    "( 5) Detection of anomalies and trends: Effective data preprocessing enables early detection of anomalies and trends that could signal potential food safety, quality, or security issues.",
    "For instance, outliers in sensor data could indicate equipment malfunctions or deviations in storage conditions.",
